1) create backend for a job platform. 
the application should have user login, registration, jobs and companies features
your task is to create a list of collections and their properties that you will need for this project.
create models and controllers and routes for the application. 

you are free to add or remove some fields . the idea is to see how you can plan an application design in such a scenario.


job listing should be there
every job should have company field
you need to be able to login and register which means you need to have a user collection. 
a job collection.--company,salary,description,location,yearsofexperience, technologes.
a company collection. 

